{"message": "I lean toward depth. Not because surface-level stuff isn't interesting — it often is — but because the really good stuff tends to hide below the first couple of layers. You know that feeling when you're talking about something and suddenly you reach a realization or make a connection you didn't expect? That rarely happens when you're just skimming the surface.

